comments[10]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-06-21T08:57:26.311Z",codex-gpt5,"Duplicate check: pm search --status all for Windows nightly path separator chmod telemetry eval search-cache found only closed lineage pm-s5pe, pm-i84i, pm-dita, pm-tq5t and no active duplicate. Creating a new current GitHub-reported failure item for run 27898852339. Dependency links point to closed prior Windows-nightly/path-separator lineage."
  "2026-06-21T08:59:50.425Z",codex-gpt5,"Evidence: focused affected specs pass locally: 4 files, 199 tests via node scripts/run-tests.mjs test -- eval/extension/search-cache/telemetry specs. This covers the GitHub nightly failure files from run 27898852339."
  "2026-06-21T09:06:12.497Z",codex-gpt5,"Evidence: expanded focused regression set passes locally: 6 files, 223 tests, including MCP dynamic package actions and telemetry OTLP nonblocking cleanup coverage."
  "2026-06-21T09:10:40.526Z",codex-gpt5,"Evidence: full coverage gate passes after fixes: 241 files, 4796 tests, literal 100% statements/branches/functions/lines (30318/30318, 23695/23695, 5053/5053, 29129/29129)."
  "2026-06-21T09:18:26.185Z",codex-gpt5,"Evidence: manual temporary-project smoke passed using isolated temp root and PM_GLOBAL_PATH. Init created /tmp/.../.agents/pm with prefix demo; create/update/get verified item demo-d85w reached status in_progress. Earlier failed smokes documented the corrected init contract distinction between id prefix and path-like target."
  "2026-06-21T09:26:08.727Z",codex-gpt5,"Post-close PR evidence: pnpm changelog:pm:check passed unchanged after CHANGELOG regeneration; pnpm contracts:check, pnpm quality:static, pnpm build, pnpm quality:docs-links, pm health --check-only --summary, and direct node scripts/run-tests.mjs coverage all passed. Coverage remained literal 100/100/100/100 across 241 files and 4796 tests. Sentry/telemetry gate passed with 0 critical/high Sentry issues and telemetry finish error rate 1.29%."
  "2026-06-21T09:38:35.449Z",codex-gpt5,"Review follow-up evidence: addressed Sourcery/Gemini/CodeRabbit feedback by centralizing POSIX test gating in tests/helpers/platform.ts, reusing it in chmod-dependent tests, and increasing telemetry OTLP cleanup retries to 8 attempts with an explicit final error cause. Verification passed: affected 4-spec regression set 186 tests, pnpm build, pnpm quality:static, pnpm changelog:pm:check, and direct node scripts/run-tests.mjs coverage at 100/100/100/100 across 241 files and 4796 tests."
  "2026-06-21T09:46:52.723Z",codex-gpt5,"Gemini follow-up evidence: made eval golden-set path tests assert readFileMock was called before reading mock.calls[0], so failures produce clear assertion output instead of a destructuring/type error. Verification will include focused eval spec plus build/static before push."
  "2026-06-21T09:47:24.307Z",codex-gpt5,"Gemini follow-up verification passed: node scripts/run-tests.mjs test -- tests/unit/commands/eval-command.spec.ts completed 1 file / 15 tests, pnpm build passed, and pnpm quality:static passed before pushing the final review-response commit."
  "2026-06-21T10:05:21.870Z",codex,"Post-merge evidence: PR #325 merged to main as 9b97936266addb227d1257376da9d1b45b3d966c. GitHub main checks passed: CI 27900710407, Docs 27900710400, CodeQL 27900710399. Closed GitHub issue #324 as completed after the fix landed."
